386
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:27,720
Ya, tuan.

387
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:28,950
Tunggu.

388
00:28:29,830 --> 00:28:30,780
Dan beritahu He Xiao

389
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:32,090
untuk berangkat segera

390
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,640
hingga 50 li di luar Longyin Pass

391
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:35,640
untuk bertemu dengan bala bantuan Zhao Che.

392
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,170
Jeneral Chu?

393
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:48,480
Jeneral Chu?

394
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,240
Jeneral Chu?

395
00:29:55,750 --> 00:29:56,610
