Buka pintu.

398
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,240
Buka pintu!

399
00:30:14,830 --> 00:30:15,880
Berhati-hati.

400
00:30:22,160 --> 00:30:23,960
Tangkap dia! Jangan biarkan dia melarikan diri!

